name: Element Contractor Farm Heavy Duty Garden Hose
description: Element Contractor Farm is a serious hose for a serious job. Whether you work on a farm, a construction site, or just around your house this hose can withstand it all. This drinking water safe hose's heavy duty reinforcement and octagonal shape give it the ultimate in burst performance and kink resistance. Ultra large, heavy duty, crush proof couplings are perfectly designed for use with a gloved hand. Larger 3/4 in. Dia delivers significantly higher water volumes than standard hoses to meet your biggest water use challenges.
